title: Rubio campaign raises nearly $6 million but sees low small-dollar donors
text: Republican presidential candidate Marco Rubio raised $5.7 million during the third fundraising quarter, according to a Federal Election Commission filing released Thursday. The Florida senator's campaign haul places him behind this quarter's heavyweight fundraisers Ben Carson and Jeb Bush, who raised $20 million and $13.4 million, respectively. Texas Sen.
